---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<section
  class="py-section-padding px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop"
  id="solutions"
>
  <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-20 items-center">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h2 class="font-headline-xl text-headline-xl mb-6">
          Un enfoque humano para datos precisos
        </h2>
        <p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-12">
          Transformamos la recolección de datos en una conversación amigable. Pulsi interactúa con
          el equipo de forma empática, garantizando una alta participación y sinceridad.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div
            class="flex gap-4 p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant bento-card relative group"
          >
            <img
              alt="Riesgos Pulsi"
              class="w-20 h-20 absolute -right-4 -top-4 hidden group-hover:block transition-all"
              src={`${base}images/riesgos.png`}
            />
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">psychology</span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-label-md text-label-md font-bold mb-1">Riesgos Psicosociales</h4>
              <p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
                Monitoreo constante de carga mental, apoyo y claridad de rol.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div
            class="flex gap-4 p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant bento-card relative group"
          >
            <img
              alt="IA Insights Pulsi"
              class="w-20 h-20 absolute -right-4 -top-4 hidden group-hover:block transition-all"
              src={`${base}images/ia.png`}
            />
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">analytics</span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-label-md text-label-md font-bold mb-1">Insights Generados por IA</h4>
              <p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
                Alertas preventivas basadas en tendencias históricas y comparativas.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div
            class="flex gap-4 p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant bento-card relative group"
          >
            <img
              alt="Monitoring Pulsi"
              class="w-20 h-20 absolute -right-4 -top-4 hidden group-hover:block transition-all"
              src={`${base}images/monitoreo_continuo.png`}
            />
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">update</span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-label-md text-label-md font-bold mb-1">Monitoreo en Tiempo Real</h4>
              <p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
                Visualiza el pulso de tu equipo minuto a minuto sin fricciones.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="flex-1 w-full bg-white rounded-3xl border border-outline-variant shadow-xl overflow-hidden p-8 md:p-12 relative"
      >
        <img
          alt="Dashboard Guide"
          class="w-32 h-32 absolute -top-8 -right-8 opacity-40 z-0"
          src={`${base}images/dashboard.png`}
        />
        <div class="space-y-8 relative z-10">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
            <span class="text-label-md font-label-md text-on-surface-variant">Pulso Semanal</span>
            <div class="flex gap-1">
              <div class="w-8 h-1 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>
              <div class="w-8 h-1 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>
              <div class="w-8 h-1 rounded-full bg-primary/20"></div>
              <div class="w-8 h-1 rounded-full bg-primary/20"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-headline-lg font-headline-lg text-center">
            ¿Cuánto esfuerzo te tomó cumplir con tu trabajo esta semana?
          </p>
          <div class="flex justify-between gap-2 overflow-x-auto pb-2">
            <button
              class="flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col items-center gap-2 p-4 min-w-[70px] rounded-xl border border-outline-variant hover:border-primary transition-colors group"
            >
              <span class="text-3xl grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all">😊</span>
              <span class="text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant">1</span>
            </button>
            <button
              class="flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col items-center gap-2 p-4 min-w-[70px] rounded-xl border border-outline-variant hover:border-primary transition-colors group"
            >
              <span class="text-3xl grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all">🙂</span>
              <span class="text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant">2</span>
            </button>
            <button
              class="flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col items-center gap-2 p-4 min-w-[70px] rounded-xl border border-outline-variant hover:border-primary transition-colors group"
            >
              <span class="text-3xl grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all">😐</span>
              <span class="text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant">3</span>
            </button>
            <button
              class="flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col items-center gap-2 p-4 min-w-[70px] rounded-xl border-primary bg-primary-container/10"
            >
              <span class="text-3xl">😟</span>
              <span class="text-label-sm font-label-sm text-primary">4</span>
            </button>
            <button
              class="flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col items-center gap-2 p-4 min-w-[70px] rounded-xl border border-outline-variant hover:border-primary transition-colors group"
            >
              <span class="text-3xl grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all">😫</span>
              <span class="text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant">5</span>
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface-container rounded-xl p-4 flex gap-3 items-center">
            <span
              class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary"
              style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">info</span
            >
            <p class="text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant">
              Un esfuerzo alto sostenido puede generar desgaste. Es importante revisarlo.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
